### Hadith 3:238

*Narrated Ibn Abbas:*

The Prophet said, "Look for the Night of Qadr in the last ten nights of
Ramadan ,' on the night when nine or seven or five nights remain out of
the last ten nights of Ramadan (i.e. 21, 23, 25, respectively)."

